templates.expansion: ⇒ Burmese: ဘတ်စ်ကား (bhatcka:)

descendants.text: ⇒ Burmese: ဘတ်စ်ကား (bhatcka:)

etymology_text: Clipping of omnibus. Formerly often spelt 'bus. The electrical sense is derived from figurative application of the automotive sense.

raw_glosses: (automotive) A motor vehicle for transporting large numbers of people along roads; by extension, the driver of said vehicle
glosses: A motor vehicle for transporting large numbers of people along roads; by extension, the driver of said vehicle
An electrical conductor or interface serving as a common connection for two or more circuits or components.
